law.history: Repealed 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 23, sec. 18, effective July 15, 1998; amended ch. 48, sec. 18, effective July 15, 1998. -- Amended 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 118, sec. 2, effective July 15, 1994. -- Amended 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 446, sec. 2, effective April 12, 1982. -- Amended 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 295, sec. 73, effective July 15, 1980. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 292, sec. 2. -- Created 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 68, Art. VIII, sec. 1, effective March 17, 1960.

metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/98). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 23 prevails over its amendment in 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 48.
